0\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569170/extras/37aa5a1cd1f2b7f9b4114e2ea6effbeb.mp4?t=1707428630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The Maze is generated randomly. You will be rewarded after beating each cell in the maze. The rewards are Skills, Items, Emblems, Gold, and Exp.<br><br></li><li> Real-time Cut-scenes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569170/extras/9ab5615d9050e0160647c46edb2d524b.poster.avif?t=1707428630\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569170/extras/9ab5615d9050e0160647c46edb2d524b.webm?t=1707428630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569170/extras/9ab5615d9050e0160647c46edb2d524b.mp4?t=1707428630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The story is told by cut-scenes and can be played again in the Gallery mode.<br><br></li><li> Character Customization!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569170/extras/dbc524705bdb57dedb1cea4330594d49.poster.avif?t=1707428630\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569170/extras/dbc524705bdb57dedb1cea4330594d49.webm?t=1707428630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569170/extras/dbc524705bdb57dedb1cea4330594d49.mp4?t=1707428630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are 6 customization slots. You can change her hair, underwear, handwear, footwear, outfit and her accessories.</li></ul>", "about_the_game": "The story begins with a missing superhero. However, the supervillain, Widow